{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"WebSocket.close()","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Konstruktor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/binaryType\"><code>binaryType</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/bufferedAmount\"><code>bufferedAmount</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/extensions\"><code>extensions</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/protocol\"><code>protocol</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/url\"><code>url</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><em><code>close()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/send\"><code>send()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ereignisse</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close_event\"><code>close</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/error_event\"><code>error</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/message_event\"><code>message</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/open_event\"><code>open</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Die Funktion <strong><code>WebSocket.close()</code></strong> beendet eine <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket</code></a> Verbindung oder den Versuch eines Verbindungsaufbaus. Wenn diese schon geschlossen ist, passiert nichts weiter.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">WebSocket.close();</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameter","title":"Parameter","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"code\"><code>code</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>Ein numerisch Wert, der den Status angibt, warum die Verbindung geschlossen wird. Wird kein Wert spezifiziert, . Zur Referenz kann <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CloseEvent#status_codes\">diese Liste mit Codes</a> des <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CloseEvent\"><code>CloseEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>s für gültige Werte genommen werden.</dd>\n <dt id=\"reason\"><code>reason</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>Ein lesbarer Text, welcher erklärt, warum die Verbindung geschlossen wird. Dieser muss UTF-8 kodiert und darf nicht länger als 123 Bytes sein.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"fehler","title":"Fehler","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"invalid_access_err\"><code>INVALID_ACCESS_ERR</code></dt>\n <dd>Ein ungültiger <code>code</code> wurde angegeben.</dd>\n <dt id=\"syntax_err\"><code>SYNTAX_ERR</code></dt>\n <dd>Der <code>reason</code> Text ist zu lang oder enthält ungültige Zeichen.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> In Gecko unterstützte diese Funktion bis zu Version 8.0 (Firefox 8.0 / Thunderbird 8.0 / SeaMonkey 2.5) keine Parameter.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Spezifikation</th>\n   <th>Status</th>\n   <th>Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a class=\"external external-icon\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/web-sockets.html#dom-websocket-close\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br>\n    <small lang=\"en-US\">The definition of 'WebSocket.close()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-Living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"api.WebSocket.close","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität"}],"summary":"Die Funktion WebSocket.close() beendet eine WebSocket Verbindung oder den Versuch eines Verbindungsaufbaus. Wenn diese schon geschlossen ist, passiert nichts weiter.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebSocket.close()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebSocket.close()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WebSocket.close()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WebSocket.close()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/websocket/close","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/websocket/close/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket","title":"WebSocket"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close","title":"WebSocket.close()"}],"pageTitle":"WebSocket.close() - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}